snippet.title: Podcast Now
snippet.description:
Podcast Now is a gaming and random discussion channel 

Daily Uploads on breaking news in the gaming and movie industry

Coverage on the biggest movies and games releasing in the form of Community Series! You may have heard about us from our Series on Batman Arkham, Pirates of The Caribbean, Star Wars, and so many more

Weekly livestreams on the biggest and newest games releasing with Alex and Kristy. 

For Business Inquires Contact Us At - podcastnow15@gmail.com

Add Us On Playstation! -  Podcast Now
